title: Eames Style Round Conference Table White/120 CM
body: In 1968, Charles Eames was able to visualize the future’s necessity to tables that will meet the needs of daily living. Thus, the Eames Round Conference Table was born. Made from high-quality and perfectly engineered materials, this Mobelaris style of Eames Style Round Conference Table combines aesthetics and practical purpose. A must-have if your interior scheme is classic and elegant. Modern classic table, sleek and simple yet unique piece to have. Truly, a remarkable Charles Eames trademark. This is a conference table that will easily impress guest and will make the room appear modern and inventive.
